{
  "page": "Black Pearl",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Black Pearl of Braavos</b> is a traditional title or name borne by a descendant of <a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys\">Bellegere Otherys</a>, the first Black Pearl, a pirate queen who became a mistress of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a>. The eldest <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> daughter of King Aegon IV and Bellegere, <a href=\"/index.php/Bellenora_Otherys\" title=\"Bellenora Otherys\">Bellenora Otherys</a>, became a <a href=\"/index.php/Courtesan\" title=\"Courtesan\">courtesan</a> under the same name. Bellenora's descendants became courtesans as well, each eventually bearing the name \"Black Pearl\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf827_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf827-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Known_Black_Pearls_.28chronological_order.29\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Black Pearls (chronological order)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Ancestry\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ancestry</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"Known_Black_Pearls_(chronological_order)\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Black_Pearls_.28chronological_order.29\">Known Black Pearls (chronological order)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Pearl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Black Pearls (chronological order)\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys\">Bellegere Otherys</a>, the first Black Pearl, pirate, smuggler, and mistress of Aegon the Unworthy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf411.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf411.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bellenora_Otherys\" title=\"Bellenora Otherys\">Bellenora Otherys</a>, the second Black Pearl, Bellegere's daughter, a courtesan.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf827_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf827-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bellonara_Otherys\" title=\"Bellonara Otherys\">Bellonara Otherys</a>, the previous Black Pearl, also a courtesan.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys_(courtesan)\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys (courtesan)\">Bellegere Otherys</a>, daughter of Bellonara, the current Black Pearl, also a courtesan.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ancestry\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Pearl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\"