e class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The first Black Pearl was <a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys\">a pirate queen</a>. A <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">prince</a> took her for a lover and got <a href=\"/index.php/Bellenora_Otherys\" title=\"Bellenora Otherys\">a daughter</a> on her, who grew up to be a <a href=\"/index.php/Courtesan\" title=\"Courtesan\">courtesan</a>. Her own daughter followed her, and her daughter after her, until you get to <a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys_(courtesan)\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys (courtesan)\">this one</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Meralyn\" title=\"Meralyn\">Meralyn</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Pearl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf827-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf827_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf827_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; The Free Cities&#32;(Braavos).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\